criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  1.solid tumor proved by pathology(d>3.0cm);

          -  2.age>18-year-old;

          -  3. Karnofsky performance status >70;

          -  4.sign the informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  1.There are obvious metal implants near the tumor;

          -  2.Can not lie still for 15 minutes.

          -  3.Pregnancy.
